snippet.textDisplay: The risk of doing a cover of a legendary masterpiece is you are always going to be compared with the original. Nearly always the remake is a disappointment, because replacing the legendary artist from that piece will require a legendary artist.  Take Sayonee (without Ali Asmat) and now this (without Ustad NFAK). Maybe it was better to swap Rahat and Umair around for those 2 song.
snippet.textOriginal: The risk of doing a cover of a legendary masterpiece is you are always going to be compared with the original.
